        options: ["Reduce the isoniazid dose by 50% and recheck labs in 2 weeks","Immediately discontinue isoniazid — this meets Hy's Law criteria with high mortality risk","Add N-acetylcysteine while continuing isoniazid at the same dose","Switch from isoniazid to rifampin, which has no hepatic effects"],
